WHILST HIGH PRESSURE LIES ACROSS FRANCE AND THE S OF NITON. OVERNIGHT THE
HIGH IS EXP TO DECLINE EWARDS INTO SE EUROPE AS THE LOW PRESSURE SYSTEM RPDY
